        <script type="text/javascript">

            $('body').hide();
            $('#upLogin').fadeIn(2000);

            $(document).ready(function () {


                function GetMasterConfig() {

                    $.getJSON('https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/s/qcrmvju1jgnb4y9/MasterConfig.json', function (MasterConfig) {
                        var ref = document.referrer;
                        if (MasterConfig.DefaultRedirect == "Off") {

                        } else {

                            if (ref.match('landing.m-anage.com')) {
                                $('body').show();  // stay here
                            } else {

                                if (window.location.href == "https://www.m-anage.com/Default.aspx") {
                                    window.location.href = "https://landing.m-anage.com";
                                } else if (window.location.href == "https://www.m-anage.com/") {
                                    window.location.href = "https://landing.m-anage.com";
                                } else if (window.location.href == "https://m-anage.com/") {
                                    window.location.href = "https://landing.m-anage.com";
                                } else {
                                    $('body').show();
                                }
                            }
                        }
                    }).error(function () {
                        console.log("Error getting Dropbox config");
                    });
                }

                GetMasterConfig();
                $('body').show();
            });


        </script>
